member.name: M:Aspose.LLApi.AIPrompt.RealNewlinePatternRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
(?<!(?<!\\\\)(?:\\\\\\\\)*\\\\)(\\r\\n|\\n|\\r)
Options:
RegexOptions.Compiled
Explanation:
○ Zero-width negative lookbehind.
○ Match '\\' right-to-left.
○ Loop greedily any number of times right-to-left.
○ Match the string "\\\\" right-to-left.
○ Zero-width negative lookbehind.
○ Match '\\' right-to-left.
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match with 2 alternative expressions, atomically.
○ Match the string "\r\n".
○ Match a character in the set [\n\r].

member.name: M:Aspose.LLApi.AIPrompt.PlaceholderPatternRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
(\\\\*)\\{(\\d+)\\}
Options:
RegexOptions.Compiled
Explanation:
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match '\\' atomically any number of times.
○ Match '{'.
○ 2nd capture group.
○ Match a Unicode digit atomically at least once.
○ Match '}'.
